Hi all lemme introduce myself I am a lvl 10 Gnome Mage on Xev server.  I really like the mage class, but one little thing that bugs the hell outta me is our choice of pets.  We have 4 to pick from.  Im a follower not a leader so I suck at making decisions, but I think I made a good plan with the help of my friend who plays a lvl 20ish rogue.  <P>SOLO PET PLAN<P>1-29=Water Pet(hey I love regen, and he just rules)<P>29-51=Fire Pet(Hey with our pet heals and buffs this little baby with his DS and DD can make quite a dent in a MOBs hp in no time, or so ive heard)<P>51-60=Whatever I get at the lvl except for 52 and 58 fire (SCREW YOU VERANT) hehe couldnt resist the 52 and 58 fire pet sucks, or so ive heard. Also hopefully 55+ ill be using my epic.<P>GROUPING PET PLAN<P>1-29=Water(Hey he kicks)<P>29-51=Air Pet(I really enjoy the stuns even when im only 10 and using the air in my derv groups sometimes, also STUNNED DORN WOOT!!!! then died 5 sec later  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>51-60=same as above<P>Well there it is my pet plan. Please post any changes or comments. Thanks in advance!<P>"Tis only a scratch"<BR>"Your arms missing"<BR>"No its not!"<BR>"Then what do you call that?"<BR>"I've had worst!"<BR>"You Lie!"<BR>Fenixil Mage of the 10 Elements<BR>Xev Server <Norrathian Wayfinders>
