Drew and Jimm have made very good points.  Drew said it best with " Situational. They're all situational."<BR>Its all about what you and your group likes.<BR>All casters group I have found that most like earth best now after the snare change ( unless ya are grouped with a necro fear kitting then air and water is what i like to use).<BR>If i were you i would use all the pets group and solo to learn each one.  At 54 I now use all my differnt pets..... I just depends on the situation that im in ( with ex of the lvl 52 fire pet dont get me started  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"> ).<BR>Hope this helps and good hunting to ya
